g.text: The deferred actions are pushed into a doubly linked list.
In mean while, the oprand and opcode are orgnazied in to a tree.
Each tree node has a pointer to parent and sibling
Here the order of the linked list matches the Post-order Traversal of the operand tree.
Candense process can visit the tree by Post-order, prepare operands at leaf node and emit Arithmetic logic operation at the parent node.
Then children node are removed and result(which is usually a reg or mem) will replace the parent node.
Following example shows how this tree be condensed.
